Issues Encountered and Resolved
Issue	Resolution
Send import error	In LangGraph 1.x, Send is imported from langgraph.types, not langgraph.graph.
HttpUrl serialization error	Changed HttpUrl to str in SourceSchema and ClaimSchema. Pydantic models are converted to dicts via .model_dump() before being returned from nodes.
Parallel update conflict	Removed current_agent from the Extractor return — parallel nodes should not all write to the same single-value field.
SessionStatus enum mismatch	Corrected status values to match the actual enum definition (running, completed).
